You can simply ask Alexa to control your Baybot Convenience Electronics “OpenAlert, MotionAlert, Live360 Camera & PetFeeder”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:

(1) Download our “Baybot” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in “Baybot” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, iOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Baybot” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Baybot” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Baybot” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

Alexa, is OpenAlert open ?
Alexa, is OpenAlert closed ?
Alexa, what is the battery on MotionAlert?
Alexa, show me the camera.
Alexa, turn on pet feeder.
Alexa, turn off pet feeder.
